    "content": "<h1 dir=\"auto\">Xiaomi-RearScreen-StarIsland</h1>\n<p dir=\"auto\">将StarIsland的超级岛同时转化到小米背屏的小组件。</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">使用方法：下载REAREye模块并激活后，导入项目压缩包，id填写pickup_flow，之后重启作用域即可。</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://github.com/juzipaome/Xiaomi-RearScreen-StarIsland/blob/main/test1.png\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"430\" src=\"https://github.com/juzipaome/Xiaomi-RearScreen-StarIsland/blob/main/test1.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 430px;\"></a>   <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://github.com/juzipaome/Xiaomi-RearScreen-StarIsland/blob/main/test2.png\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"430\" src=\"https://github.com/juzipaome/Xiaomi-RearScreen-StarIsland/blob/main/test2.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 430px;\"></a></p>"
